{"tid":875491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[發下夢啦] 如果比你中左六合彩頭獎，你會實現咩夢想？人生會點過？","createTime":"2018-10-25T02:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T15:46:39.000Z","uid":34475,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"123dc3b108c4c0e448a3af77721e6a36275112ed","tid":875491,"uid":34475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">請唔好講投資炒樓滾大舊錢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">講有咩你一直想做，但因為工作、家庭呢d現實因素搞到做唔到既</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我既話，肯撚定辭職先，即刻俾一大舊錢老母任佢洗<br />\n之後認真報班學鋼琴同報班學日文<br />\n隨時去世界同地旅行，唔洗怕貴機票旺季問題<br />\n日文學到一定程度，就去日本周圍流浪，體驗風土人情，甚至向當地買番間屋可以隨時住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n向香港既時候，屎忽痕就讀下d鐘意既課程(社會人文、心理犯罪) 唔洗驚考試fail，我為興趣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行街買衫食野唔洗再睇價錢，買餸唔洗去街市同人迫，可以去高級超市，唔洗等d野就過期、有特價先買，唔洗行幾間黎格價etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入會每日做gym，身體健康都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就咁幻想下都覺得生活好充實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後會法國宜家既人生完全唔係自己想過既，完全唔知做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦，發完夢啦，我繼續做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdff74991c4e7817fbf94e393c4e0593db7f6b5f","tid":875491,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97f9533781e2c7cfeba87a31929b8dd5480f417e","tid":875491,"uid":156121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:46:16.000Z","msg":"買個home studio<br />\nSet 哂所有我鍾意既console同pc<br />\n隔音 加個電子琴<br />\n<br />\n開youtube/twitch channel<br />\n日日打機<br />\n<br />\n冇人睇都冇所謂"},{"pid":"29c2ee72f0533369ce8ce455740e6c553802e9fc","tid":875491,"uid":139187,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,